<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Aquora | Save Our Seas</title>

<style>
* {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    font-family: "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
}

body {
    background: #0b1e2d;
    color: white;
    line-height: 1.6;
}

header {
    padding: 20px 10%;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
}

header h1 {
    color: #00d4ff;
}

nav a {
    color: white;
    margin-left: 20px;
    text-decoration: none;
}

.hero {
    height: 90vh;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: 20px;
}

.hero h2 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.hero span {
    color: #00d4ff;
}

.hero button {
    padding: 12px 25px;
    border: none;
    background: #00d4ff;
    color: black;
    font-size: 16px;
    cursor: pointer;
    border-radius: 5px;
}

.section {
    padding: 80px 10%;
    text-align: center;
}

.section h2 {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: #00d4ff;
}

.cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 30px;
}

.card {
    background: #102c3d;
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 10px;
}

footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px;
    background: #08141d;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
    <h1>Aquora</h1>
    <nav>
        <a href="#problem">Problem</a>
        <a href="#solution">Solution</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
</header>

<section class="hero">
    <h2>Protect Our Oceans with <span>Aquora</span></h2>
    <p>Real-time water monitoring to save marine life</p>
    <button onclick="scrollToSection()">Learn More</button>
</section>

<section id="problem" class="section">
    <h2>The Problem</h2>
    <p>Polluted water blocks sunlight, destroying marine ecosystems and coral reefs.</p>
</section>

<section id="solution" class="section">
    <h2>Our Solution</h2>
    <div class="cards">
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Scout</h3>
            <p>Measures pH and turbidity in real-time underwater.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h3>AquaTalkie</h3>
            <p>Receives data and sends alerts, warnings, and advice instantly.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="contact" class="section">
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Email: your@email.com</p>
</section>

<footer>
    <p>© 2026 Aquora. Save Our Seas.</p>
</footer>

<script>
function scrollToSection() {
    document.getElementById("problem").scrollIntoView({behavior: "smooth"});
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
